   <li><p>Create a Signature client. </p></li> 
   <li><p>Get the PDF document that contains the signatures to verify. </p></li> 
   <li><p>Set PKI run-time options.</p></li> 
   <li><p>Retrieve all digital signatures.</p></li> 
   <li><p>Iterate through all signatures.</p></li> 
  </ol> 
